author: mikeshardmind(Sinbad)
name: NoAdmin
short: Prevent commands from being used in servers that give the bot admin rights.
description: Prevent commands from being used in servers that give the bot admin rights. This still allows it if the guild owner is also a bot owner to prevent stupidity related lockouts.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not persistently store data or metadata about users.
